{"tid":135372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台妹 力挺「普教中」：英語、普通話 沒高低之分","createTime":"2017-02-26T10:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T13:41:01.000Z","uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5bf36bc7c99caafd5215fd5a36b04fb7fb46ed2c","tid":135372,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T10:09:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zv88s4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZv88s4.jpg&h=b23d149b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【#中大乜乜乜之我想問&hellip;&hellip; 06】 <br />\n<br />\n有台灣女生想問：「<span style=\"color: red;\">我地都係講普通話，點解剩係開廣東話?堂</span>？:3」 <br />\n<br />\n這台灣女生的名字叫婉吟，日本研究系一年級，對語言很感興趣，正在學阿拉伯語和廣東話。訪問時會突然問：「咦，這個字廣東話怎樣唸？」連白板上問題，也是用廣東話寫的。就算對語言這麼感興趣，<span style=\"color: red;\">她還是覺得普通話開的課程太少了</span>，「你知道嗎，像UGFN，只有一班是講普通話的。除了特殊科系（中文系），廣東話的課還是佔大多數。」 <br />\n<br />\n台灣同學婉吟則有不同的觀察：「因為有內地生而改為以普通話授課的例子，我沒有聽過，<span style=\"color: red;\">因國際生而改用英語授課倒是有</span>。其實我現在還沒有上過用普通話教的課，大部份都是英語的，只有體育課用廣東話。」 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「我也是說普通話的，如果只用廣東話教課，那我怎樣辦呢？例如本地生（中文口語有一定水平）和台灣學生要上課討論，普通話是一種大家都能溝通的語言，為甚麼不用？有國際生的課會轉用英語，也是一樣呀。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">普通話跟英文並沒有高低之分</span></span>，我認為<span style=\"color: red;\">尊重對方而使用不同語言是一件體貼的事</span>。&rdquo;When you speak another person&rsquo;s language, you speak into their hearts.&rdquo; 而且那不妨礙我去學習廣東話呀。」"},{"pid":"39d8f5e4d5ff830dba351db6e18ff5e640660015","tid":135372,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T10:10:14.000Z","msg":"又loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aba4eb9804c0c4e1494fd3e6ebed1b92d70a768","tid":135372,"uid":82727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T10:10:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d61a71c44216c3344b910508b4e0657f8fa54293","tid":135372,"uid":58247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T10:14:30.000Z","msg":"咁北京大學台灣大學有無廣東話泰文越南話?"},{"pid":"31446df3994173b357040f5fa79862987af7c32a","tid":135372,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T10:29:39.000Z","msg":"因為普教中會多左啲政治意識既野 即係呢...關佢撚事咩"},{"pid":"6eda92ec824e99a83840a59cbd8641edb5369041","tid":135372,"uid":44187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T10:37:34.000Z","msg":"呢度喺香港啊"},{"pid":"d2fd2d67cac76822a17dd7eb22190ceacf6e8f42","tid":135372,"uid":6076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T10:38:56.000Z","msg":"不爽不要讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb4395ef6389651dd7e4b0d25dc307c4abc7796","tid":135372,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T11:04:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45fe05370313dd0e8a997a41cfdca9551a3a1840","tid":135372,"uid":53769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T11:10:31.000Z","msg":"戇柒鳩"},{"pid":"5611e42423d464a73a335dae46bb42e09a23a2a5","tid":135372,"uid":9200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T11:42:16.000Z","msg":"去到台灣係咪又開埋廣東話班比我地呀？"},{"pid":"79053aeb66fc869c51cac80a751a80f640719dc8","tid":135372,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T11:44:58.000Z","msg":"樓主係反粵，分化港台五毛狗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sy7L780.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsy7L780.jpg&h=d839a87f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/26/194456_aafb5d8d8ea4d4e517a98d23e15b1d56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F26%2F194456_aafb5d8d8ea4d4e517a98d23e15b1d56.jpg&h=168896ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a6c21a35c315f4563e4523319ecde2e4b0e6612","tid":135372,"uid":32150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T13:41:01.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - 酒吞童子 )"}]}